	<h1 class="title">亚马逊也想找“广场舞大妈”送货，这事能成吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/43366/small/43366.jpg?1430896699" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王民超 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-06-19 10:11:10 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/10948/medium/10948.jpg?1436644371" alt="" />			
	</div>
